data.title: Full List Of Canadian Folk Music Award Nominees 2021
data.meta_description: The Canadian Folk Music Awards are an annual music awards ceremony presenting awards in a variety of categories for achievements in both traditional and contemporary folk music, and other roots music genres, by Canadian musiciansTHE CANADIAN FOLK MUSIC AWARDS  ANNOUNCE 2021 NOMINEES 100 nominees in 19 categories from across CanadaTraditional Album of the Year • Le Diable à Cinq - Debout! • Bruce Cockburn - Crowing Ignites • Ian & Sylvia - The Lost Tapes • Pharis & Jason Romero - Bet On Love • Be
data.text: The Canadian Folk Music Awards are an annual music awards ceremony presenting awards in a variety of categories for achievements in both traditional and contemporary folk music, and other roots music genres, by Canadian musicians
